After some time, Adam gets tired of [[masturbating]] and bitches to God, who gives Adam [[roofies]] and makes Eve out of one of his ribs. When an evil snake, (supposedly [[Satan]] if you're a Christian, if you're Jewish then it's just a fucking snake) persuaded the Eve to eat the forbidden fruit, the pair were [[banhammer|banned]] from the Garden of Eden for all eternity. This is the origin of the Christian  opinion [[Fact|that women are inferior to men]]. God installs the first firewall in front of the Garden of Eden using some hardc0re angels.

